{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "阿尔贝里亚骑士道 赛希尔的秘密",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "哈尔揭露了赛希尔帝国时代的种种恶行。\\n内疚不已的赛希尔在利弗的呵斥下，\\n终于直面自己的正义与骑士道。\\n利弗将教会骑士交给赛希尔对付，\\n为与哈尔做个了断而提出单独对决。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "以狄涅尔皇帝之名，\\n对傲慢之龙予以制裁。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "龙",
            "context": "咕啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵1",
            "context": "不愧是赛希尔大人！\\n连龙都能斩杀！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "森林化为灰烬也是早晚的事。\\n皇帝之命已经完成，迅速撤离。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（这样就好……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵2",
            "context": "听说雷古塔村\\n和罗南镇都毁了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵3",
            "context": "因为赛希尔大人斩杀了\\n那里的守护龙吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵2",
            "context": "失去守护龙的地方会魔力紊乱，\\n水源枯竭，人就没法住了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵3",
            "context": "所以赛希尔大人\\n才不用火烧周边城镇吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵2",
            "context": "是啊，应该是为了节省人力吧。\\n不愧是优秀的人才。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（我这么做没有错……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（就算脏了自己的手，\\n也不能离开王的身边。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（为了拯救王，就要一直\\n待在离王最近的地方……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（这样一来……总有一天，\\n会有机会的！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "我一直对此坚信不疑，\\n然而——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "哈尔！你让开！\\n我也要和陛下同行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "那可不行，能继续前进的\\n只有皇帝陛下和塞西娅大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "你身为近卫，是要违抗\\n陛下的命令吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "就算受到责罚我也要去！\\n我要保护陛下才行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（总觉得心神不宁……\\n有一股不祥的预感……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "哈尔，你再碍事的话\\n就算打倒你也要……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "暗龙的咆哮",
            "context": "唔嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "这咆哮声，难道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "看来一切……都结束了呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "怎么会……骗人……骗人的……\\n陛下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "当我赶到时，\\n陛下已经驾崩。\\n我明明就在那里，\\n却没能救下他。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "为了救亚罗拉斯王……\\n我不惜牺牲众多性命。\\n然而——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊啊啊……对不起……\\n对不起……我……我……\\n全都、全都杀光了，对不起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔！\\n你振作点，赛希尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "这有什么可哀叹的？\\n你不过是完成了你敬爱的王——\\n不，应该说是皇帝之命而已啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "没想到赛希尔\\n也参与了猎龙行动……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "这不是什么稀奇事吧？\\n而且我也参与了\\n将龙魔兽化的实验……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "哦，利弗你被降级调职，\\n所以才不知道这件事吧。\\n对吧，赛希尔？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……\\n魔、魔养石……魔养石……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "现在正谈要紧事呢，\\n竟然要吃东西，\\n太不懂礼貌了……吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "哎呀，你要袒护她？\\n她可是扰乱你口口声声\\n要守卫的祖国和平之人呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "可说来也真滑稽。\\n你为了王不惜四处猎龙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "到头来只剩下毁灭的村落……\\n王也死了。啊……多么悲惨。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊……啊啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔，别听他胡说！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "舍弃骑士正义行善的自尊，\\n还没能对王尽忠……\\n这样的你还能从头来过？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "一个连自己的理想都无法守护的人，\\n谈什么守护新主啊。\\n还妄图心怀希望，真是厚脸皮。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "是啊……我……\\n不配当骑士……我，不能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "对不起……\\n对不起……陛下……\\n呜……呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "赛希尔已经动不了了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "教会骑士们，作战开始。\\n一举歼灭在森林出口\\n待命的白燕骑士团。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗雷德",
            "context": "休想！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "这是我要说的才对。\\n哼！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗雷德",
            "context": "唔啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "弗雷德！\\n哈尔，你这家伙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "利弗，别轻举妄动。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "不然无论是赛希尔还是你的部下，\\n甚至那些人质的生命安全\\n我都无法保证哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120043_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵&老板娘",
            "context": "噫！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "呃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "对不起……对不起……\\n我什么都保护不了……对不起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔，别这样！\\n不要苛责自己！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "可是……我什么都没能守护……\\n还害了民众和龙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "没能守护和你们谈论的理想……\\n连陛下都……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "不！\\n有你守住的东西！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "骗人……骗人骗人！\\n哪有……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔，不要迷失了自我！\\n无论你怎么否定，\\n也的确有你守住的东西！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "那就是……你的正义。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "正义？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "我还以为你要说什么……\\n原来扯到守护正义上了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "呵呵……真是滑稽！\\n没想到你是这么\\n阴险的人物呢，利弗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "眼睁睁看着龙、民众还有王\\n被杀的行为，你管它叫正义？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "是、是啊……\\n我已经毫无正义可言……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "那你为什么在哭泣？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "你无法赞同残忍的行径，\\n但是——正因为如此\\n你才会感到痛苦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "无论你染指多少恶行，\\n你内心的正义也不曾消失。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "正因为你希望自己行得端坐得正，\\n你才会烦恼、挣扎、受伤，\\n甚至不愿回首过去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "你那失意的泪水正是\\n你内心正义尚存的证明！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我们最后的底线是“内心的正义”。\\n只要这份正义还在，不管什么情况\\n都能贯彻骑士道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "内心的正义……\\n骑士最后的底线……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我感到的后悔……\\n就是我的……正义？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（如果我内心的正义尚存，\\n就能再次踏上骑士道吗……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（这一次……\\n能够实现理想吗……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01",
                "120015_01",
                "120043_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "老板娘",
            "context": "赛希尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（不！这次我一定要实现理想！\\n保护好应当守护之人！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120043_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士2",
            "context": "呃啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0084",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "各位！趁现在快逃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0085",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0086",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "利弗……谢谢你。\\n多亏了你，我终于能够面对……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0087",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "面对我内心的正义……\\n面对我的骑士道！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0088",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "是吗……\\n那这些人就交给你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0089",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "嗯……我会保护好老板娘他们的。\\n教会骑士就交给我对付吧。\\n相对地……你懂的吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0090",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "嗯……我要在此打倒哈尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0091",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "呵呵呵……好啊，\\n有本事就来吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0092",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "看在同窗一场的份上，\\n就由我来粉碎——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0093",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "你们那虚无缥缈的\\n骑士道吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_05_0094",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}